description:
Your guide to Shrek Forever After

The ultimate guide to the summer's biggest movie is yours to own from 1st July! Find out all about Shrek Forever After, meet the characters, and find out which Shrek character you are most like! The comic is packed full of fun features, comic strips, puzzles, and the chance to win a Nintendo Wii with the Shrek Forever After game!

The Parent Trap

Shrek's parents pay their son a visit in one of two hilarious new comic strips featuring in Totally... Shrek Forever After. It seems they've arrived just in time to teach their grandchildren about their heritage - ogres are supposed to be repulsive and terrifying, not cute and adorable!

Top Donkey Moments

He has a song for every occasion and more one-liners than you can shake a stick at! Check out the new movie's funniest Donkey moments!

Find the treasure!

Dragon and Donkey's babies have wandered off from their parents - now it's up to you to follow the clues and help find them!

Make your own Gingy

Follow in the footsteps of the Muffin Man and make your own Gingy. Cute and delicious - just the way we love our baked goods!
name: Shrek Forever After

description:
The official magazine of the ITV1 smash hit adventure series Primeval, featuring an awesome mix of creature features, comic strip action and all the best bits from the latest series!

The Story So Far

Find out what's happened since dinosaurs suddenly started turning up across Great Britain - and the government recruited a research team to investigate the sightings!

Meet The Cast!

Who's who in Primeval - and what do the show's actors think about the characters they play?

Dinosaur Survival Plan

Ever wondered how you would cope with the anomalies of Primeval? Just follow our simple steps and you'll never be a dinosaur's dinner!

Awesome Comic Strips

Matt reaches new heights on the south bank of London in 'Eye Strain', and Jess and Becker encounter a T-Rex in a modern art gallery in ‘Picture This’!

Behind the scenes

Some sneaky snaps of the Primeval team - as you've never seen them before!

How Primeval Are You?

Take our test to find out which of the ARC team your personality is most like!

Plus:

  • A competition to win official Primeval books and complete series DVD boxsets!
  • Puzzles, activities and quizzes
  • Predators of Primeval feature
  • Pull-out posters!
  • Make a Pterosaur and draw your own prehistoric monster!

Build Your Own Tyrannosaurus Rex and Primeval stickers!
name: Primeval

description:
Totally: The Phantom Menace is a one-off, 32-page official movie souvenir magazine that celebrates all things Star Wars: The Phantom Menace with a galaxy of features, puzzles, and games. And to mirror the movie’s exciting new dimension, it features ten pages in amazing 3D, including an all-new, all-action comic strip! There’s an eye-popping double page 3D pull-put poster with some of the most iconic characters in cinema brought to life!

Free Gifts: C-3PO Grabber Arm, 3D Glasses + Stickers!

Duel of the Fates

An awesome comic strip in eye-popping 3D! Anakin, still a slave boy, shows his speedy Podracing in Tatooine, while Darth Maul crushes battle droids and is trained up by the dreadful Darth Sidious!

All about Darth Maul

Darth Maul is the mysterious evil at the heart of Star Wars: The Phantom Menace - but we delve into his past to shed some light on his dark power in this special feature.

Jedi Training

A Jedi Knight is one of the coolest warriors in the galaxy - who wouldn't want to fight with a lightsaber? Discover the trials you must face if you want to be accepted into the Jedi Order!

Movie Magic

The Phantom Menace is a movie packed with stand out scenes, but after much debate, we count down the top five moments!

Make your own Lightsaber!

The final test before becoming a Jedi is to build your own lightsaber! If you want to join the ranks of the galaxy's greatest warriors, follow our step-by-step guide to construct your very own lightsaber!

Plus:

  • Amazing 3D The Phantom Mencace pull-out poster!
  • Win LEGO Star Wars sets and Darth Maul Double-Bladed Lightsabers
  • Cut out and make your own Darth Maul mask!
  • Jar Jar's Ha Ha's: The Phantom Menace jokes
  • Awesome The Phantom Menace puzzles and activities!
name: Star Wars Episode I: The Phantom Menace

The fateful climax of ‘Shadowland’ is here! A possessed Daredevil clashes with the Ghost Rider! Matt Murdock faces his greatest challenge in a shocking finale!

By Andy Diggle and Billy Tan.

Also: Amadeus Cho and Thor match wits with the diabolical Vali Halfling in a quest across the mythical realms of the Marvel Universe!

By Greg Pak, Fred Van Lente and Reilly Brown.

Includes material reprinted from Shadowland #5 and Prince of Power #3-4.

Tokyo trembles as Hope and the new mutant generation take on the mad artist Kenji!

Also: The X-Men fall victim to a mysterious illness, and Cyclops is forced to place Utopia Island under quarantine. But the sinister Lobe has the answer: a brand new team of X-Men!
